---
---

<section id="learn" class="what-you-learn">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-heading">What You'll Learn</h2>

    <div class="cards-grid">
      <article class="session-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <path d="M12 16v-4"></path>
              <path d="M12 8h.01"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Foundations</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="card-framing">
          Shared context and practical skills for people with no technical background.
        </p>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li><strong>What AI actually is</strong> — algorithms, data ownership, evaluating tools</li>
          <li><strong>Community perspectives</strong> — what Alliance members are already doing</li>
          <li><strong>Basic tooling</strong> — command line, code editors, AI assistants</li>
          <li><strong>Evaluating any tech stack</strong> — who owns and controls what</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="session-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"></path>
              <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Deep-Dives</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="card-framing">
          Co-designed with members. Led by practitioners building in this space.
        </p>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Local model deployment and federated data</li>
          <li>Open-source agent frameworks</li>
          <li>Knowledge mobilization — moving community knowledge into interoperable formats</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="session-card session-card--support">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="icon-wrapper icon-wrapper--green">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Support & Mapping</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="card-framing">
          Ongoing access to help — and mapping the ecosystem across Canada's bioregions.
        </p>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Weekly drop-in office hours and coworking</li>
          <li>Scheduled one-on-one calls for focused problem-solving</li>
          <li>Technical sensemaking for founders and leads</li>
          <li>Asset mapping and knowledge graphing of the Alliance ecosystem</li>
          <li>Connecting members to bioregional and domain-specific knowledge commons</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .what-you-learn {
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-cream-light);
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .session-card {
    background-color: var(--color-cream);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.1);
    transition: transform var(--transition-medium),
      box-shadow var(--transition-medium);
  }

  .session-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.12);
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background-color: var(--color-orange);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .icon-wrapper--green {
    background-color: var(--color-green);
  }

  .icon {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card-framing {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .card-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card-list li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    padding-left: 1em;
    position: relative;
  }

  .card-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.55em;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-green);
  }

  .card-list li strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .what-you-learn {
      padding-block: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .session-card {
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }

    .icon-wrapper {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
    }

    .icon {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .session-card {
      transition: none;
    }

    .session-card:hover {
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>
